00:16:49.010 --> 00:16:52.050
But whether you do it within
the discretion you have,

00:16:52.050 --> 00:16:54.170
it's a rulemaking, or whether you
do it through statutory reform,

00:16:54.170 --> 00:16:57.110
I think these distinctions
