00:18:12.740 --> 00:18:14.090
in that computer program.

00:18:14.090 --> 00:18:15.950
We have to make distinctions
somehow.

00:18:15.950 --> 00:18:19.110
The other point I wanted
to make originally was

00:18:19.110 --> 00:18:23.550
that there were a number
of comments to the effect

00:18:23.550 --> 00:18:25.970
