questions, but if everybody agrees

01:12:35.320 --> 01:12:37.120
that the Copyright Office

01:12:37.120 --> 01:12:42.510
and Register Librarian do not
have the power to grant exemptions

01:12:42.510 --> 01:12:47.020
with respect to trafficking,
then why worry about giving

01:12:47.020 --> 01:12:52.230
that appearance in the course of
legitimately acting on a petition

01:12:52.230 --> 01:12:55.980
for exemption that is before you?

01:12:55.980 --> 01:13:03.290
