01:20:18.970 --> 01:20:20.670
&gt;&gt; Kevin Amer: -- Technology
Act that's been proposed.

01:20:20.670 --> 01:20:24.010
Mr. Love, did you have--

01:20:24.010 --> 01:20:25.410
[ Inaudible Remark ]

01:20:25.410 --> 01:20:26.710
&gt;&gt; Andrew Moore: Yeah, sorry.

