commerce that could be used

01:25:25.710 --> 01:25:28.610
to infringe could be prohibited.

01:25:28.610 --> 01:25:33.470 position:56%
And the Court articulated a standard
that talked about not wanting

01:25:33.470 --> 01:25:37.270
to see prohibition
affecting articles that were--

01:25:37.270 --> 01:25:39.590
could be used to infringe
but were capable

01:25:39.590 --> 01:25:41.940
